Very sweet but not fruity. It reminds me of when I used to eat the fruit in the summer time. So refreshing and sweet. It's a touch of summer! I have to try not to lick it away when I apply it on my lips. Review Title: This is by most one of my favorite flavors because it tastes JUST like the fruit Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: SALE! Lighted Makeup Mirror for Travel and Home 10x 1x Vanity Mirror with BONUS Eyebrow Tweezers Review Date: 2015/09/10 Average Rating: 3.2 Product Details: {'Package Dimensions': '5.2 x 4.8 x 2.2 inches; 12 Ounces'} Review Text: This is an unique mirror. I have yet to see one like this. The mirror came with a standard tweezer. Not the best but can't complain.

It is very well made and high quality. There are two mirrors; enlargement and normal. Very well designed for applying makeup because of light.
A good size. Neither too big or small. Travel friendly and great for those messy desks ;)
Adjustable and very light weigh.

The mirror has 3 slots for batteries. To open the cover on the bottom you have to turn the circular plate.
Three slides for lighting option; top mirror light, and bottom. It's not necessary but totally awesome.
I can't get over this mirror!

Discount received for the mirror for testing and reviewing purpose. All of my reviews are 100% honest and unbiased. Thank you for reading! Review Title: Woh. Check it out Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Moroccan Argan Oil Shampoo, 8 Fl Oz - Smooths and Repairs - Sulfate Free - Natural - Imported from Morocco by Pure Body Naturals Review Date: 2016/03/03 Store: Pure Body Naturals Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Pure Body Naturals', 'Item Form': 'Oil', 'Hair Type': 'All, Color Treated', 'Scent': 'Coconut', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Product Dimensions': '3.9 x 5.91 x 5.91 inches; 8 Ounces', 'UPC': '646437736398 646437319751'} Review Text: I have long black hair and of medium thickness. The length is up to my belly button which is consider very long. It's hard to manage sometimes because I don't like shampoo that weighs my hair down or make them tangled.

This argan oil shampoo smells very good but I prefer something that is not scented with chemicals which are labeled as "parfum"
The scent don't really bother me. The texture is nice and not too thick. Lathers up my hair nicely with a quarter size. Since I have a lot of hair, I have to use a quarter size or more. I scratch and rub my scalp for about 30-50 seconds before I rinse in a bucket. This helps me to clean my hair even better. Instead of just rinse form the shower, which dandruff can still stick in my hair.
I am quite impressed with the result. My hair is not too dry not oily at all but moisturized. It feels silky with some volume and smells great. Review Title: It's hard to manage sometimes because I don't like shampoo that weighs my hair down or make them ... Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Seya Beauty Pro Makeup Train Case with Dual Tray Removable & Adjustable Plastic Dividers (Black with Silver Trim) Review Date: 2018/10/30 Store: Seya Average Rating: 4.3 Product Details: {'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '15.3 x 9.5 x 9 inches; 6.05 Pounds', 'Item model number': 'TS04SBKF', 'UPC': '784190959972'} Review Text: This case is extremely sturdy with a downfall: it's too heavy.
It has these two closures but there is no security because there is no code pad or lock. The trays opens up which adds an organized compartment. Review Title: Plenty of room Rating: 3.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: WEBEAUTY Makeup Brushes Set 10 Pieces Premium Synthetic Foundation Brush Blending Face Powder Blush Concealers Eye Shadows+ Bonus Blender Sponge + Brush Egg + Travel Makeup Bag (10+3pcs) Gift For Lady Review Date: 2018/11/01 Store: WEBEAUTY Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Brand': 'WEBEAUTY', 'Recommended Uses For Product': 'For Concealing, For Blush, For Foundation', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Item Form': 'Wand', 'Number of Pieces': '10', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Ferrule Material': 'Aluminum', 'Skin Tone': 'All', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '9.9 x 5.2 x 1.9 inches; 10.41 Ounces', 'UPC': '772629967834'} Review Text: These are your basic and pretty much must haves makeup brushes. The tips are soft and blends well. The sponge is for blending as well. Mainly for foundations. The brushes are for powder, etc. This set would be a perfect holiday or birthday gift to any ladies. Review Title: Basic makeup brush set Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Mesaidu 3-in-1 Eye Makeup Eyebrow Pencil, Blender, Brush All In One (Acorn)… Review Date: 2018/12/05 Store: Mesaidu Average Rating: 3.8 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Mesaidu', 'Item Form': 'Gel', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Item Weight': '0.04 Pounds', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '6.6 x 0.6 x 0.6 inches; 0.64 Ounces', 'UPC': '605945934993'} Review Text: This is an essential eyebrow pencil combo. It has 3 parts; blender, pencil and brush. The pencil has a twist and draws on smoothly. The blender helps to blend out any sharp edges. The brush gives my eyebrow some color, making it more intense. Review Title: 3 in 1 Rating: 5.0 --------------------------------------------------

SUMMARY:  
The individual exhibits a clear preference for high-quality and effective personal care and beauty products, often favoring brands that prioritize natural ingredients. Their consistently positive ratings, particularly for products like lip balm and hair care, indicate a strong preference for nourishing, hydrating, and pleasant-scented items. Sentiments reflect a longing for products that evoke enjoyable experiences, reminiscent of seasons and natural elements.  

Across purchases, there is a recurring theme for multifunctional items, as seen with the dual-purpose makeup mirror and 3-in-1 eyebrow pencil. This suggests a lean towards practicality and efficiency in their beauty regimen. Moreover, the user appears to be sensitive to price, valuing discounted offers while still aiming for higher-quality goods, hinting at a preference for affordability without compromising on performance.  

Overall, the core preferences highlight a blend of quality, effectiveness, and practicality in personal care products, alongside a proclivity for items that enhance the overall beauty experience while being mindful of value.
